message.content: "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE". This paper proposes a new framework for named entity recognition using machine reading comprehension, which falls under the intersection of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques (cs.IR) and specifically focuses on named entities (cs.NE).
